title: Did A Ghost Move Hide These Items? | True Ghost Stories
description:
Today on another haunting episode of Real Ghost Stories Online.

We all do it. 

As we go through our days, sometimes, we tend to misplace things. 

Often times by our own doing. 

But what happens when objects, sometimes, very important items, go missing with no explanation. 

Almost vanishing into thin air? 

Today, we hear the haunting story of this mysterious phenomenon in action, on Real Ghost Stories Online.
